{"2203290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "駭獸少女", "steam_appid": 2203290, "required_age": "20", "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/商店頁__1_.png?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「乖乖把你的根源之力交給我吧！」</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>怪物的身軀不斷被緊壓、勒緊，直到皮膚再也壓制不住從裡面往外爆發的壓力…… </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>臟器、肉塊還有無數肌肉組織，從被捏爛的身軀噴發出來。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>同時，也噴了我一臉的鮮血。 </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/商店頁__8_.png?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>而我是誰、究竟為什麼會在這裡，「駭獸」又是什麼…… </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>這些疑問在尚未得到解答之際，一陣反胃感逼得我跪在地上不斷乾嘔。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>正想起身時，我只感到眼前一黑…… </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「加塔諾托亞，是個科學家。 」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/商店頁__9_.png?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「最終回合。」</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >結合探索、蒐集、養成、以及傳統回合制戰鬥與戰位影響等要素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓玩家能夠培育自己的駭獸、打造出專屬於自己的戰術</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與各種充滿魅力的魔物娘邂逅發展關係</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大量的動態CG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收錄大量鴉醬老師繪製的精緻CG，挑逗你內心深處的繁殖慾望！甚至還有可控的互動體驗！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>『多線世界』的文本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像是翻開一本本交錯的小說，每條支線都是一段等待被傾聽的故事，每個岔路都藏著不為人知的秘密與命運。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/內文動圖01.gif?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多樣的角色設計</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色皆有獨特的背景故事與技能，和她們建立深厚感情。 <br>展開屬於你們的冒險，觸發各種「特殊事件」…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸的完整語音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全劇情配音，使每位角色形象更加立體，也為玩家提供更深一層的遊戲體驗。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/Story_EP1_Pious01_1A-_1_.gif?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/Story_Ep1_Elymas01_2B_AtoQ-Idle_M.gif?t=1756455239\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/EP1_Confession_01B_AtoE-Idle_D.gif?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>豐富的遊戲系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是想要瞭解故事與角色、戰鬥打怪、培養感情、蒐集資源、或是單純的繁殖…… 一次滿足所有玩家對於遊戲內容的各種期待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>熱血的戰鬥體驗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選角、選招、出招！每一步都影響戰局走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配多種互動式 Buff 與專屬絕招動畫，打出屬於你的華麗一擊！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203290/extras/商店頁__5_.png?t=1756455239\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/